<strong>Website:</strong> <a href="http://www.thepensionsregulator.gov.uk/">http://www.thepensionsregulator.gov.uk</a><br />
<br />
The Pensions Regulator took over from Occupational Regulatory Authority on 6 April 2005.
</p>
